This is a docker based implementation of a search engine with rpc's

To resolve dependencies:
go mod tidy

To run:
docker compose build --no-cache
docker compose up -d coordinator
go run .
docker compose up -d client

To cleanup:
docker compose down

*if you don't have the docker desktop, you can forcefully close and clear the containers with this
 docker rm -f $(docker ps -aq --filter "name=rpc-worker")